# ==================================================================
# LeafClient .gitignore — partial open-source policy
# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# The repo intentionally exposes ONLY the C#/Java source code
# (Models, Services, ViewModels, Views/*.axaml.cs, Utils, Program.cs)
# Every artifact, asset, build output, secret, IDE cache, internal
# doc, infra script, and runnable binary is hidden so the repo
# cannot be compiled/run locally and no infrastructure is leaked.
# ==================================================================


# ==================================================================
# OS / System files
# ==================================================================
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Icon?
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
ehthumbs_vista.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/
*~
*.swp
*.swo


